  <groupId>org.nuxeo.ecm.platform</groupId>
  <artifactId>nuxeo-platform-imaging-convert</artifactId>
  <name>Nuxeo Platform Imaging Convert</name>
  <description>
    Nuxeo Platform Imaging provides picture management to Nuxeo Web Platform
    and RCP. It offers minor picture transformation like rotation or resizing.
    Imaging-Convert is a plugin for nuxeo convert service. Available
    converter provides rotation, resizing and cropping for the
    following image types: JPEG, GIF, BMP, TIFF. PNG is sadly not supported
    yet.
  </description>

